		<div class="cell grid-x latest-story-container">
											<div class="cell auto tertiary-story">
					<div class="story-img-container">
						<a href="https://lithub.com/notable-literary-deaths-in-2025/" title="Notable Literary Deaths in 2025"><img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/sunsetatsea-300x300.jpg"></a>
